<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM5.9">
<l>paiṅkiḷi vaṇṇaṉ cirītara ṉeṉpatōr pācat takappaṭṭi runtēṉ</l>
<l>poṅkoḷi vaṇṭiraik kumpoḻil vāḻkuyi lēkuṟik koṇṭitu nīkēḷ</l>
<l>caṅkoṭu cakkarat tāṉvarak kūvutal poṉvaḷai koṇṭu taruta</l>
<l>liṅkuḷḷa kāviṉil vāḻak karuti liraṇṭat toṉṟēl tiṇṇam vēṇṭum.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I have been caught up in a snare called Śrīdhara, the green parakeet-hued [Lord].</l>
<l>O koel that live in the grove where the abundantly resplendent bees clamour!</l>
<l rend="indent">Listen to this in a focused way!</l>
<l>If you consider living in these groves,</l>
<l>[you] will surely be required to [do] one of the two [things]:</l>
<l rend="indent">crying so that He with the discus and the conch comes</l>
<l rend="indent">[or] bringing gold [my lost] bracelets.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
